T1  - Informational Shocks, Off-Label Prescribing, and the Effects of Physician Detailing
AU  - Shapiro, Bradley T.
Y1  - 2018/01/19
PY  - 2018
DA  - 2018/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2017.2899
